'''Lubed''' was a slang word that was used by [[Ben Skywalker]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] to mean something that was good or "cool." It became popular among people of Ben's generation, much to the irritation of [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]], his mentor at the time.<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Betrayal">''[[Legacy of the Force: Betrayal]]''</ref>

